{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-15942/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-15942"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:59:42"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Angle"]},"value":{"none":["low"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["mobile, handheld"]}},{"label":{"none":["Composition"]},"value":{"none":["two shot"]}}],"summary":{"none":["Man and woman kiss"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15942/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-15942","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15942/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-15942"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15942/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15942/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15942/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15942/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15942/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15942/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15942/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15942/canvas/1/80be6d8a-3b33-463f-a585-d63473c81efa","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:08:45.991Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>While the “Phantom Thead” theme from Jonny Greenwood’s score, with its haunting viola and muted piano, has until now been deployed to signal discordance in Reynolds and Alma’s relationship, it now sounds out to acknowledge their deep love and twisted romance.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15942/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:28.489132025348027,37.534247792529385,297.8640378311111,207.2474507720639"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15942/canvas/1/fb7798b5-0505-4076-8ed9-29f7f51af4c5","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:09:06.924Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>According to lighting cameraman Mike Bauman, this scene originally involved a more elaborate lighting cue that would be triggered when Reynolds asks Alma to kiss him. What remains in the film are the remnants of this lighting (Lux Lighting, “<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"Hyperlink SCXW252743736 BCX4\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kpi393XkzUo\"><u>Lighting Phantom Thread</u></a>”).&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15942/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:33.79934210526308,296.32177033492815,294.49162679425837,197.23833732057426"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15942/canvas/1/21110f50-22f5-496a-9a9b-398ede152dd3","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-30T17:09:21.923Z","creator":"Ada ","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>While the kiss begins with Reynolds above Alma, leaning down to kiss her, he moves so that he is beneath her by the end of it, signaling his willing submission to her.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-15942/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:562.3744019138755,46.39952153110041,980.6339712918659,782.2652511961722"}}}]}]}]}